    {
      "type": "desc",
      "contents": []
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Give ear, O my people, to my teaching; incline your ears to the words of my mouth! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Give ear, O my people, to my teaching; incline your ears to the words of my mouth!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I will open my mouth in a parable; I will utter dark sayings from of old, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I will open my mouth in a parable; I will utter dark sayings from of old,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "things that we have heard and known, that our fathers have told us. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "things that we have heard and known, that our fathers have told us."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We will not hide them from their children, but tell to the coming generation the glorious deeds of the Lord, and his might, and the wonders that he has done. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We will not hide them from their children, but tell to the coming generation the glorious deeds of the Lord, and his might, and the wonders that he has done."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We will not hide them from their children, but tell to the coming generation the glorious deeds of the Lord, and his might, and the wonders that he has done."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He established a testimony in Jacob and appointed a law in Israel, which he commanded our fathers to teach to their children, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He established a testimony in Jacob and appointed a law in Israel, which he commanded our fathers to teach to their children,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He established a testimony in Jacob and appointed a law in Israel, which he commanded our fathers to teach to their children,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "that the next generation might know them, the children yet unborn, and arise and tell them to their children, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "that the next generation might know them, the children yet unborn, and arise and tell them to their children,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "so that they should set their hope in God and not forget the works of God, but keep his commandments; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "so that they should set their hope in God and not forget the works of God, but keep his commandments;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "so that they should set their hope in God and not forget the works of God, but keep his commandments;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "and that they should not be like their fathers, a stubborn and rebellious generation, a generation whose heart was not steadfast, whose spirit was not faithful to God. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "and that they should not be like their fathers, a stubborn and rebellious generation, a generation whose heart was not steadfast, whose spirit was not faithful to God."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "and that they should not be like their fathers, a stubborn and rebellious generation, a generation whose heart was not steadfast, whose spirit was not faithful to God."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The Ephraimites, armed with the bow, turned back on the day of battle. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The Ephraimites, armed with the bow, turned back on the day of battle."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They did not keep God’s covenant, but refused to walk according to his law. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They did not keep God’s covenant, but refused to walk according to his law."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They forgot his works and the wonders that he had shown them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They forgot his works and the wonders that he had shown them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "In the sight of their fathers he performed wonders in the land of Egypt, in the fields of Zoan. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "In the sight of their fathers he performed wonders in the land of Egypt, in the fields of Zoan."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He divided the sea and let them pass through it, and made the waters stand like a heap. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He divided the sea and let them pass through it, and made the waters stand like a heap."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "In the daytime he led them with a cloud, and all the night with a fiery light. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "In the daytime he led them with a cloud, and all the night with a fiery light."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He split rocks in the wilderness and gave them drink abundantly as from the deep. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He split rocks in the wilderness and gave them drink abundantly as from the deep."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He made streams come out of the rock and caused waters to flow down like rivers. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He made streams come out of the rock and caused waters to flow down like rivers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yet they sinned still more against him, rebelling against the Most High in the desert. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Yet they sinned still more against him, rebelling against the Most High in the desert."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They tested God in their heart by demanding the food they craved. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They tested God in their heart by demanding the food they craved."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They spoke against God, saying, “Can God spread a table in the wilderness? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They spoke against God, saying, “Can God spread a table in the wilderness?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He struck the rock so that water gushed out and streams overflowed. Can he also give bread or provide meat for his people?” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He struck the rock so that water gushed out and streams overflowed. Can he also give bread or provide meat for his people?”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He struck the rock so that water gushed out and streams overflowed. Can he also give bread or provide meat for his people?”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Therefore, when the Lord heard, he was full of wrath; a fire was kindled against Jacob; his anger rose against Israel, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Therefore, when the Lord heard, he was full of wrath; a fire was kindled against Jacob; his anger rose against Israel,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Therefore, when the Lord heard, he was full of wrath; a fire was kindled against Jacob; his anger rose against Israel,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "because they did not believe in God and did not trust his saving power. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "because they did not believe in God and did not trust his saving power."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yet he commanded the skies above and opened the doors of heaven, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Yet he commanded the skies above and opened the doors of heaven,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "and he rained down on them manna to eat and gave them the grain of heaven. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "and he rained down on them manna to eat and gave them the grain of heaven."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Man ate of the bread of the angels; he sent them food in abundance. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Man ate of the bread of the angels; he sent them food in abundance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He caused the east wind to blow in the heavens, and by his power he led out the south wind; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He caused the east wind to blow in the heavens, and by his power he led out the south wind;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "he rained meat on them like dust, winged birds like the sand of the seas; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "he rained meat on them like dust, winged birds like the sand of the seas;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "he let them fall in the midst of their camp, all around their dwellings. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "he let them fall in the midst of their camp, all around their dwellings."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And they ate and were well filled, for he gave them what they craved. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And they ate and were well filled, for he gave them what they craved."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But before they had satisfied their craving, while the food was still in their mouths, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But before they had satisfied their craving, while the food was still in their mouths,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "the anger of God rose against them, and he killed the strongest of them and laid low the young men of Israel. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "the anger of God rose against them, and he killed the strongest of them and laid low the young men of Israel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "the anger of God rose against them, and he killed the strongest of them and laid low the young men of Israel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "In spite of all this, they still sinned; despite his wonders, they did not believe. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "In spite of all this, they still sinned; despite his wonders, they did not believe."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So he made their days vanish like a breath, and their years in terror. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "So he made their days vanish like a breath, and their years in terror."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When he killed them, they sought him; they repented and sought God earnestly. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When he killed them, they sought him; they repented and sought God earnestly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They remembered that God was their rock, the Most High God their redeemer. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They remembered that God was their rock, the Most High God their redeemer."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But they flattered him with their mouths; they lied to him with their tongues. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
